 but he won't call me. 

802
01:04:00,010 --> 01:04:01,800
 Seok Ji Won... 

803
01:04:01,800 --> 01:04:04,950
 He must hate me now. 

804
01:04:04,950 --> 01:04:08,800
 He must hate me over what happened because of my family. 

805
01:04:09,290 --> 01:04:11,590
 Seok Ji Won? 

806
01:04:15,960 --> 01:04:18,980
 What do I do, Ji Hye? 

807
01:04:19,890 --> 01:04:23,030
 I miss him so much... 

